title: Sketching at Home and Abroad - British Landscape Drawings, 1750-
description:
Sketching at Home and Abroad - British Landscape Drawings, 1750-1850
Pierpont Morgan Library | 1994 | English | 68 pages | PDF | 7.4 MB


This is a brief exhibition catalogue of " Sketching at Home and Abroad-British Landscape Drawings 1750 to 1850 Shown at the Pierpont Morgan Library in 1992.

There are 3 essays
The Development of the English Watercolour E J Phimister
The Picturesque Landscape
Turner Girtin and the Rise of Romanticism

The are notes and a bibliography . Also a checklist of the 116 items in the exhibition- the annotations to the check list are brief
